# 6. Backend Components

## Event Controller

Responsibilities

* Receives frontend requests
* Calls business services
* Returns responses

Example responsibilities

* Load leaderboard
* Add team
* Remove team
* Update score

---

## Team Service

Purpose

Manages team data.

Responsibilities

* Create teams
* Delete teams
* Retrieve teams
* Validate team information

Methods

```
addTeam()

removeTeam()

findTeam()

getTeams()

teamExists()
```

---

## Score Service

Purpose

Controls all scoring logic.

Responsibilities

* Increase score
* Decrease score
* Reset competition
* Calculate rankings

Methods

```
increaseScore()

decreaseScore()

resetScores()

sortLeaderboard()
```

---

## Registration Service

Purpose

Processes new registrations.

Responsibilities

* Import registrations
* Validate team data
* Prevent duplicates
* Create Team objects

Methods

```
loadRegistrations()

createTeam()

validateRegistration()

registerTeam()
```

---

## Firebase Service

Purpose

Communicates with Firebase Realtime Database.

Responsibilities

* Save teams
* Save scores
* Retrieve scores
* Listen for updates

Methods

```
connect()

getTeams()

saveTeam()

updateScore()

deleteTeam()

listenForChanges()
```

---

## Google Sheets Service

Purpose

Retrieves registration information.

Responsibilities

* Read spreadsheet
* Parse rows
* Convert rows into Team objects

Methods

```
loadSheet()

parseRows()

extractMembers()

convertToTeams()
```

---

## Countdown Service

Purpose

Calculates registration countdown.

Responsibilities

* Calculate remaining time
* Determine registration status

Methods

```
getRemainingTime()

isRegistrationClosed()

formatTime()
```

---

## QR Code Service

Purpose

Provides registration QR code.

Responsibilities

* Generate QR image
* Link QR to registration form

Methods

```
generateQRCode()

getRegistrationURL()
```

---

## Authentication Service

Purpose

Controls administrator access.

Responsibilities

* Validate administrator password
* Create authenticated session
* Reject invalid access

Methods

```
login()

logout()

validatePassword()
```

