Example structure

```json
{
  "scores": {
    "team001": {
      "name": "Dominant FC",
      "score": 80
    },
    "team002": {
      "name": "The All Stars",
      "score": 65
    }
  }
}
```

Benefits

* Real-time updates
* Cloud persistence
* Multi-device synchronisation
* Automatic refresh

